bcmath-desc: Provides arbitrary-precision arithmetic to Lua modules
bcmath-check-self-nan: “self” does not have a valid value
bcmath-check-operand-nan: operand “$1” does not have a valid value
bcmath-add-opposite-infinites: Adding two infinite values of opposite direction
bcmath-add-similar-infinites: Adding two infinite values of similar direction
bcmath-sub-opposite-infinites: Subtract two infinite values of opposite direction
bcmath-sub-similar-infinites: Subtract two infinite values of similar direction
